I move to amend House Bill No. 3386 as follows:
1. On Page 1, Line 11 ½, by inserting a new section to read as follows:
“Section 1. NEW LAW A new section of law not to codified in the Oklahoma Statutes reads as
follows:
This Act shall be known and may be cited as the “Prohibiting Landlords from Removing Tenants
Who Haven’t Paid Their Rent Act”.;
2. Renumbering subsequent sections; and
2. Amending the title to conform.
